  <brief_title>The RATIO: Registry of Infections and Lymphoma in Patients Treated With TNF-a Antagonists</brief_title>
  <official_title>The RATIO Registry: French Registry on Opportunistic and Severe Bacterial Infections and Lymphoma in Patients Treated With TNF-a Antagonists</official_title>
