  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria for cases:

          -  past or current treatement with TNF-a antagonists

          -  either lymphoma severe bacterial infection opportunistic infection

        Inclusion Criteria for controls:

          -  matched with cases by gender, age (+/- 5 years), underlying disease (rheumatoid
             arthritis, ankylosing spondylitis, Crohn's disease, or psoriasis)

          -  past or current treatement with TNF-a antagonists

          -  no lymphoma, severe bacterial infection, opportunistic infection (same as case)

        Exclusion Criteria:
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
